# Blender backups
*.blend1
*.blend1.meta

# Memory captures & recordings
Shattered Realms/[Mm]emoryCaptures/
Shattered Realms/[Rr]ecordings/

# JetBrains Rider
Shattered Realms/[Aa]ssets/Plugins/Editor/JetBrains*
*.DotSettings.user

