*.app

crashlytics-build.properties

# TestRunner scenes
Shattered Realms/InitTestScene*.unity*

# Addressables
Shattered Realms/ServerData
Shattered Realms/[Aa]ssets/StreamingAssets/aa*
Shattered Realms/[Aa]ssets/AddressableAssetsData/link.xml*
