# Custom ignores (your paid & private assets)
Shattered Realms/[Aa]ssets/Art/
Shattered Realms/[Aa]ssets/Synty/
Shattered Realms/[Aa]ssets/Prefabs/

# TextMesh Pro (installed inside Assets → MUST be ignored)
